728011f-b.title: Queens: Springfield Boulevard - Murdock Avenue
728011f-b.text:
Springfield Boulevard, west side. at Murdock Avenue, showing
one of the Hendrickson houses. In 1891 it was owned by Ino. C.
Hendrickson and in 1918 by C. Tracy. Thia was also known as the
Werner farmhouse. See other views on Springfield Road for other
Hendrickson homes.
1922
Views 1,2,5
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
